        <h2 class="w600">Spontaneous differentiation of buffalo (Bubalus bubalis) embryonic stem cells towards germ cell lineage</h2>
        <div data-dropdown="a1" data-options="is_hover:false" class="custom-tootip-head">
          <p class="pt5 mb10 f14 author-title"><i class="fa  fa-dot-circle-o pr5 small-font text-lite-green"></i>&nbsp;Syed Mohmad Shah<sup>#,*</sup>,</p>
